544
00:50:31,160 --> 00:50:35,870
God damn it! What are you doing?
You leave me here!

545
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:39,350
Get away.
Just leave me here! Get out!

546
00:50:39,440 --> 00:50:42,955
God, I said leave me here,
God damn it!

547
00:50:43,040 --> 00:50:45,429
