- I'll be all right.

562
00:52:24,320 --> 00:52:27,073
Come on. Come on. Come on.

563
00:52:31,640 --> 00:52:33,392
I'm OK, Forrest.

564
00:52:36,200 --> 00:52:38,077
I'm OK. I'm fine.

565
00:53:13,200 --> 00:53:16,112
Top smoke. Get it up there.

566
00:53:16,320 --> 00:53:20,393
If I'd have known this was going
to be the last time me and Bubba

567
00:53:20,480 --> 00:53:23,756
was gonna talk, I'd of thought
of something better to say.

568
00:53:23,840 --> 00:53:27,719
- Hey, Bubba.
- Hey, Forrest.

569
00:53:29,880 --> 00:53:35,796
- Forrest, why did this happen?
- You got shot.

570
00:53:36,760 --> 00:53:41,072
Then Bubba said something
I won't ever forget.

571
00:53:41,160 --> 00:53:43,799
I want to go home.

572
00:53:44,640 --> 00:53:47,996
Bubba was my best good friend.

573
00:53:48,080 --> 00:53:52,596
And even I know that ain't something
you can find just around the corner.

574
00:53:52,680 --> 00:53:55,797
Bubba was going to be
a shrimping boat captain,

575
00:53:55,880 --> 00:54:00,112
