00:54:19,720 --> 00:54:23,235
Yes, sir.
Bit me directly in the but-tocks.

580
00:54:23,320 --> 00:54:27,472
They said it was a million
dollar wound, but...

581
00:54:27,560 --> 00:54:29,516
