01:00:24,400 --> 01:00:28,075
I understand you were wounded.
Where were you hit?

640
01:00:28,160 --> 01:00:29,752
In the but-tocks, sir.

641
01:00:29,840 --> 01:00:34,197
Well, that must be a sight.
I'd kinda like to see that.

642
01:00:46,560 --> 01:00:48,312
God damn, son!

643
01:00:51,160 --> 01:00:54,357
After that, Mama went
to the hotel to lay down,

644
01:00:54,440 --> 01:00:58,228
so I went out for a walk
to see our capital.

645
