01:07:47,080 --> 01:07:51,631
She told me about
all the travelling she'd done

718
01:07:51,720 --> 01:07:55,349
and how she discovered
ways to expand her mind

719
01:07:55,440 --> 01:08:00,798
and learn how to live in harmony,
