720
01:08:00,880 --> 01:08:04,429
'cause she made it
all the way to California.

721
01:08:05,680 --> 01:08:09,593
Hey. Anybody
want to go to San Francisco?

722
01:08:09,680 --> 01:08:12,638
- I'll go.
- Far out!

723
01:08:12,720 --> 01:08:16,633
It was a very special night
for the two of us.

724
01:08:18,360 --> 01:08:20,271
I didn't want it to end.

725
01:08:21,360 --> 01:08:25,592
- Wish you wouldn't go, Jenny.
- I have to, Forrest.

726
01:08:27,160 --> 01:08:31,836
Jenny?
Things got a little out of hand.

727
01:08:32,520 --> 01:08:36,672
It's just this war and that lying
son of a bitch Johnson and...

728
01:08:38,080 --> 01:08:40,833
I would never hurt you.
You know that.

729
01:08:43,480 --> 01:08:45,471
Know what I think?

730
01:08:47,360 --> 01:08:52,354
I think you should go home
to Greenbow, Alabama!

731
