And in China,
they never go to church.

757
01:11:54,320 --> 01:11:58,871
- No religion, too?
- Hard to imagine.

758
01:11:59,400 --> 01:12:02,472
Well, it's easy if you try, Dick.

759
01:12:02,560 --> 01:12:05,757
Some years later,
that nice young man from England

760
01:12:05,840 --> 01:12:10,516
was on his way home to see his little
boy and was signing some autographs.

761
01:12:10,600 --> 01:12:14,912
For no particular reason at all,
somebody shot him.

762
01:12:17,320 --> 01:12:21,199
They gave you
The Congressional Medal of Honour.

763
